snippet.title: Peck N Run Trailer - peck off on the 17th September!
snippet.description:
A prototype game made with a group of interns, we tied it up with a bow and want to see if you love it - if you do, we'll put time and money into taking it to the next level!

Spilt Milk Shake is a label for experimental and unfinished games made by Spilt Milk Studios.

You can find them on itch: https://spiltmilkstudios.itch.io/
